    <section class="plan-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">1</div>
                <div>
                    <span class="section-label">Phase One</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Universal Transition Support</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plan-content">
                <div class="plan-text">
                    <p>Every worker displaced by AI automation deserves a safety net that provides security while they transition to new opportunities. This isn't charity‚Äîit's an investment in human potential and economic stability.</p>
                    <p>We advocate for legislation that requires companies deploying AI to contribute to a national transition fund, ensuring those who lose jobs aren't left to fend for themselves.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-features">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">‚úì</div>
                        <span>Income replacement at 80% of previous salary for up to 2 years</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">‚úì</div>
                        <span>Healthcare continuation during the entire transition period</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">‚úì</div>
                        <span>Housing stability protections against displacement</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="feature-icon">‚úì</div>
                        <span>Career counseling and job placement services</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="plan-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">2</div>
                <div>
                    <span class="section-label">Phase Two</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Massive Retraining Investment</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plan-content">
                <div class="plan-text">
                    <p>The skills needed for tomorrow's economy are different from today's. We need a national commitment to education and retraining that treats learning as a lifelong journey, not something that ends after school.</p>
                    <p>This means free access to quality education and training programs, delivered in ways that work for adults with families and responsibilities‚Äînot just traditional college students.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-features">
