                    <span class="section-label">Phase Three</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">New Job Creation</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plan-content">
                <div class="plan-text">
                    <p>While some jobs will disappear, new opportunities must be created‚Äîespecially in areas that AI cannot replace and that benefit society. We advocate for public investment in sectors that serve human needs.</p>
                    <p>These new jobs should be good jobs: well-paid, with benefits, and offering dignity and purpose. We can create millions of positions in caregiving, education, environmental restoration, and community development.</p>
                </div>
